text.tspan: Once the game has started, your ships can't be moved.
A better score means a smaller amount of shots you used to win the game.
Sink your opponent's ships before it sink yours!
You have 5 ships,: a Carrier (5), a Battleship (4), a Cruiser (3),
Ships can only be placed vertically or horizontally , and can't overlap.
You start. You pick a target on the top grid, guessing where the computer's boats are.
The computer will let you know if you MISS, HIT or SUNK their boat.
If you win the game, the game will record your score and keep a collection
The computer then takes its turn to shoot at you. Then it's your turn again.
